                                        Program for detecting the largest variety of
                                        music formats available for the AMIGA.
                                        Detection is possible in both a dynamic
                                        buffer you can read any data to and in
                                        specified valid system memory ranges. - 88
                                        different Sound formats can be detected.
                                        
